Renames the USB-MIDI product string the 16U2 enumerates as, from the
upstream default "MocoLUFA" to "VAMP Loopstation" (loopy's pedal is the
VAMP unit). Apply against dualMocoLUFA's Descriptors.c before building —
see firmware/README.md.

Upstream: https://github.com/kuwatay/mocolufa (Apache License 2.0)

--- a/Descriptors.c
+++ b/Descriptors.c
@@ -453,9 +453,9 @@
 /* for MIDI */
 USB_Descriptor_String_t PROGMEM ProductStringMIDI =
 {
-	.Header                 = {.Size = USB_STRING_LEN(8), .Type = DTYPE_String},
+	.Header                 = {.Size = USB_STRING_LEN(16), .Type = DTYPE_String},

-	.UnicodeString          = L"MocoLUFA"
+	.UnicodeString          = L"VAMP Loopstation"
 };

 /** This function is called by the library when in device mode, and must be overridden (see library "USB Descriptors"
